data.description: Welcome to this Charming, One-of-a-kind property with great INCOME POTENTIAL This 3/2 home in the heart of Fort Myers is a short walking distance to the iconic McGregor blvd, lined with beautiful palm trees. The city just re-paved the streets leading to the home. As you pull up to the deep 6 car driveway, you’ll instantly be struck by the majestic oak tree & Charming walkway, that adds to the historic character of the home. The inside has a real fireplace, 2 living rooms, brand new completely renovated guest bath, modernized kitchen with stainless steel appliances & granite countertops. Pool deck area is completely screened with a Rare oversized pool. Feels like there are 2 back yards. Home boasts a BONUS SIDE EFFICIENCY w/ separate Entrance & exit, private yard, extra bathroom and kitchenette making this truly a 4/3 home. This can be especially alluring for turning that part of the home into an income-generating opportunity as a vacation rental or for family use as a in-law suite or multi-generational living. Side efficiency has its own mini split ice cold AC unit & a new electric water heater. Roof 10 years old. NO FLOOD ZONE, SAVE THOUSANDS!
